N2  - A reexamination of the methods and subjects of theory is proposed. Organizational scholars are urged to avoid big business organizations and to examine, instead, everyday events, places, and questions, micro-organizations, and absurd organizations. In these sites, organizationally relevant phenomena are more visible and available for hypothesis generation than in complex organizations.
